thread.title: Sandra
thread.title_full: Wall Art Prints reviewed by Sandra

author: Sandra
title: Sandra
text:
I couldn't be more happy with my purchases, there is stuff always on sale and I even got $10 off on top for signing up to the newsletter (you can always unsubscribe after).
The website is great, it even gives you suggestions if you want to pair up a canvas which is what I ended up doing.
Shipping is free and super fast as well, it only took 5 business days to get delivered and everything comes really well packaged.
